Citrix Systems - Wikipedia






















 






Citrix Systems

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with Cyrix.

Citrix Systems, Inc.





Citrix Systems headquarters in Santa Clara, California




